Minister Dionisio Perez-Hacome gives details of the disaster that killed Interior Minister Francisco Blake and seven others.
The Ministry of Communications and Transport (MOTC) said the results of the accident, which killed Interior Minister Francisco Blake Mora and seven others, showed that the helicopter hit the ground in perfect health without the pilot attempting an emergency landing.
