"Two large organisations in France have pledged to systematically distribute contactless cards to their customers in the future", said Gerard Neboui, CEO of Visa Europe France.
Banks are testing mobile payments.
But this is only the first step in the development of the future payment method, which is the mobile phone.
So far, only a few devices are equipped with the NFC technology needed to make such transactions.
